product_summary: The NMRV Worm Gearbox Motor is a high-efficiency gear box motor designed for various industrial applications. It features a power rating of 0.06KW, 0.09KW, 0.12KW, 0.18KW, 0.25KW, 0.37KW, 0.55KW, 0.75KW, 1.1KW, 1.5KW, 2.2KW, 4KW, 5.5KW, 7.5KW, 11KW, and 15KW. It is available in IEC flange sizes 56B5, 56B14, 63B5, 63B14, 71B5, 71B14, 80B5, 80B14, 90B5, 90B14, 100B5, 100B14, 112B5, 112B14, 132B5, 160B5. The gearbox offers a reduction ratio of 1:7.5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 40, 50, 60, 80, and 100. The housing is made from die-solid aluminum alloy for RV25-RV90 and die-cast solid iron for RV110 to RV150. The worm is made from 20CrMnTi with carburizing and quenching, and the surface harness is 56-62HRC. The shaft is made from chromium steel-45#. The gearbox is available in blue, silver, or other colors as per customer requirements. It is suitable for omnibearing installation and offers high radiation efficiency and good service life. The product is manufactured in China and comes with a 1-year warranty.
